org.libex.concurrent

Class TimeSpan

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.libex.concurrent.TimeSpan
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<TimeSpan>

    @ParametersAreNonnullByDefault
@ThreadSafe
@Immutable
public final class TimeSpan
extends Object
implements Comparable<TimeSpan>
    Specifies a period of time. The idea for this class was taken from the Guava Issues post 631. http://code.google.com/p/guava-libraries/issues/detail?id=631
    Author:
    John Butler
